divs: Sighting DetailsI was letting my dog out. It was dark out and I seen this bright round object in the sky. It was moving very slowly across the sky, in a funny manner. I yelled for my husband and went to get my camera. We watched it move up and down. I did get one picture then, I went back in the house to get the settings right on my new camera and when I came back outside it was gone.
Object Flight Path: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
